BriefDescription: Counts the number of times an HLE XACQUIRE instruction was executed inside an RTM transactional region.
Counts the number of machine clears due to memory order conflicts.
PublicDescription:
This event counts the number of memory ordering Machine Clears detected. Memory Ordering Machine Clears can result from one of the following:
1. memory disambiguation,
2. external snoop, or
3. cross SMT-HW-thread snoop (stores) hitting load buffer.
